    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine and is completely free of any scratches, dents, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin looks and smells like new, with premium materials that show no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, offering a smooth, powerful ride with all systems functioning exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a car in pristine, collector-quality condition.",
