    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface, mechanical component, and electronic system operates at its absolute peak, reflecting a history of uncompromising stewardship. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard used market. Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence.",
