    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey guys! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty! I have babied this car since day one, and it is honestly in pristine, showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell! I'm truly sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it. Come check it out and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
